# knowledge.md

Global personal knowledge base. Auto-loaded at the start of every session.
Apply preferences and patterns found here without being asked.

**Setup:** Add this file to opencode.jsonc instructions:

```jsonc
{
  "instructions": ["~/.agents/knowledge.md"]
}
```

**Agent instructions:**

- This file is auto-loaded — no need to read manually
- Append new entries when cross-project preferences or patterns are identified
- Never overwrite existing entries
- Keep entries concise — 3 to 5 lines maximum per entry

